{"tid":629001,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"邊吵架邊打交 卻又「點到即止」美俄敘利亞對壘做戲做全套","createTime":"2018-04-14T10:48:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-14T12:34:23.000Z","uid":174649,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fa08c96bbc0f5c573ff442515227949c764f616d","tid":629001,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T10:48:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1360198/org/16b533b8e016c5c6a83197f18e666719.jpg/J7Cl6D3UAz2qUxIRpusbAN4CfNr2TH0wTFInQUxSJ0E?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1360198%2Forg%2F16b533b8e016c5c6a83197f18e666719.jpg%2FJ7Cl6D3UAz2qUxIRpusbAN4CfNr2TH0wTFInQUxSJ0E%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=a7d37b57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國、英國及法國於香港時間今早9時向敘利亞發射多枚戰斧巡航導彈，打擊「與化武相關設施」，令敘利亞局勢再度升溫。可是發射導彈的動作雖大，實際作用有多少仍然成疑。<br />\n<br />\n與此同時，敘利亞藉着此前俄羅斯部署的防空設備，第一時間攔截13枚導彈。俄羅斯國防部更第一時間表示，美英法三國導彈都沒有進入俄羅斯防空區域。<br />\n<br />\n這場「邊吵架邊打交」的對壘，在美國和俄羅斯相互拼硬的同時，從各方就最新發展的公布，似乎都未有將戰爭全面升級的打算，打出來的聲勢或許只是逼不得已。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"280ec421a709211b1c48ded59ebdc69610b8b12c","tid":629001,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T11:01:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2EI7sZ3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2EI7sZ3&d=McwV6t0VOKXoNwRu14ZqnwRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=600163a4\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2EI7sZ3</a>"},{"pid":"e8e927e7983d5707039f011dde325dba37f34ede","tid":629001,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T11:10:30.000Z","msg":"做比邊個睇？"},{"pid":"2dfdf88a33706fa83873f977dd32327ac1a315d3","tid":629001,"uid":126590,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T11:17:03.000Z","msg":"又摑連登仔一巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n俾邊個睇？咪就係連登成班傻仔囉，做下樣又信到十足<i